    • Enum Constant Summary

      Enum Constants 
      Enum Constant and Description
      AttributeAssignment
      The value was expanded due to an attribute assignment which had been lost and is being reprovisioned.

      The value was expanded due to evaluation of a provisioning policy on an application.
